{"tid":795914,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC新龍之谷] 歡迎來到我的秘密花園 [4]","createTime":"2018-08-27T11:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T11:33:37.000Z","uid":6654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"283c8128e9f2644a8bc98c7e47b337d9057bc51b","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:13:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ilHRinm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FilHRinm.png&h=bc7b3ef5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歡迎來到新龍之谷討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">台港澳版 新龍之谷係一款大型多人線上角色扮演遊戲，自2010年開始由遊戲橘子代理，直到2013年易手俾 遊戲新幹線 作為現今唯一台港澳版 新龍之谷<span style=\"color: red;\">總</span>代理商。</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yqinXl3-grQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyqinXl3-grQ&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=2a281636\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yqinXl3-grQ</a></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">相信大部分連登仔對龍之谷都唔陌生，佢始終都係3D第3人稱遊戲經典中嘅經典，奈何時代遺忘咗佢，係時候一齊回谷搵翻失去咗嘅回憶同爽快嘅打擊感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></div></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><del><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">最重要係角色好J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></del></div></span><br />\n<br />\n <div style=\"text-align: center;\">台灣遊戲新幹線 新龍之谷官網: <br />\n<a href=\"http://dn.gameflier.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdn.gameflier.com&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=703dff41\" target=\"_blank\">http://dn.gameflier.com</a><br />\n香港GAMEONE 新龍之谷官網(十年冇更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ): <a href=\"http://dn.gameone.com/index.php?show=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdn.gameone.com%2Findex.php%3Fshow%3D1&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=9306f97b\" target=\"_blank\">http://dn.gameone.com/index.php?show=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有關於新龍之谷的公告請查閱台灣遊戲新幹線 新龍之谷官網</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n職業系統:<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰士</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/I7fZzzf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FI7fZzzf.png&h=b440129c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-劍聖-<br />\n劍鬥士<br />\n月光劍豪<br />\n<br />\n-傭兵-<br />\n狂戰士<br />\n毀滅者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">弓箭手</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Xww650O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXww650O.png&h=fd375788&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-箭神-<br />\n天弓射手<br />\n馭魔箭手<br />\n<br />\n-遊俠-<br />\n影舞者<br />\n風行者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">魔法師</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rQn3E1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrQn3E1c.png&h=5ef2fc0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-元素使-<br />\n炎之幻姬<br />\n冰之女王<br />\n<br />\n-魔導士-<br />\n光影術士<br />\n時空領主<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">牧師</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QewAERR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQewAERR.png&h=3341f469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-賢者-<br />\n聖騎士<br />\n十字軍<br />\n<br />\n-祭司-<br />\n聖徒<br />\n審判者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">機甲蘿莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3WEA89c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3WEA89c.png&h=55230da0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-機甲召喚師-<br />\n砲擊之星<br />\n機甲司令<br />\n<br />\n-鍊金術師-<br />\n鍊魔使<br />\n鍊癒使<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">卡莉</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rgFFH9v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrgFFH9v.png&h=125b8bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-靈喚舞姬-<br />\n暗黑召喚師<br />\n喚靈使者<br />\n<br />\n-媚影舞孃-<br />\n劍刃舞者<br />\n闇影支配者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">刺客</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jfmZqVp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjfmZqVp.png&h=863ab789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-追擊者-<br />\n掠奪者<br />\n撕裂者<br />\n<br />\n-使者-<br />\n光輝使者<br />\n深淵行者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">蘭希亞</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ev3Ki58.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEv3Ki58.png&h=b810ea41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-奪魂者-<br />\n疾風魅影<br />\n幻魔槍騎<br />\n<br />\n-槍術師-<br />\n冰霜舞姬<br />\n緋紅戰姬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">瑪奇娜</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/g2ncJWy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fg2ncJWy.png&h=446d4bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n-機甲獸孃- <br />\n破壞者 <br />\n捍衛者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">外傳職業呢? </span><br />\n暗黑復仇者<br />\n銀月獵手<br />\n黑暗異教徒<br />\n暗黑法師<br />\n縱雷機師<br />\n天羽神姬<br />\n噬血閽靈<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">一般都唔建議玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你會問邊隻角色最勁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>答: 月光 物槍 暗刺 3大幻神</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[center]<span style=\"color: gold;\">新手建議:</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">不論您係初次玩、定回流者，應該多開幾個角色，慢慢體會隻game既樂趣，比對唔同角色嘅優點缺點，從而搵到您玩得最開心最順手既職業，先課金玩落去為佳，令龍谷更具耐玩性，避免恨錯難返。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div>"},{"pid":"edda6f65f6d47bee3e0d54f16db0e9fbed176c10","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:14:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 你哋咩SERVER?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n答: 台港澳同一個程式，入面所有伺服器亦已經全部合併，揀邊個都冇問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. GF+ 同 GAMEONE 有咩分別?</span><br />\n答: 基本上只有課金用唔同點卡的分別，GF用MYCARD，GAMEONE用GO卡。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 點解唔見咗舊AC嘅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n答: 由於垃圾遊戲橘子結束代理營運，2013年11月11日或以前的遊戲帳號已經被刪除， 所以一律要在遊戲新幹線/ Gameone 重開始新一個遊戲帳號。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 4. 唔見你介紹下職業特色嘅? </span><br />\n答: 唔想個PO變咗字海同具爭議性問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果想特別問某職業就回覆問啦，會有專人解答<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(吹奏)</span></span>你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5. 裝備問題</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">答: <br />\n現時封頂係95LV<br />\n暫時最勁既裝係95L4階+20 台服只有一把<br />\n95A&gt;95S&gt;95S2&gt;95L&gt;95L2&gt;95L3&gt;95L4<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他裝備資訊參考龍谷內置的封頂指南<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</div> <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 5. 滿終係幾多? </span><br />\n答: <br />\n95Lv:14944<br />\n<br />\n終傷計算機:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Nnha4oqxEsJP_Zqz0cW0M6nKNO6gVI-g0V-iL_Dn7fk/edit#gid=674767160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1Nnha4oqxEsJP_Zqz0cW0M6nKNO6gVI-g0V-iL_Dn7fk%2Fedit%23gid%3D674767160&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c2544125\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Nnha4oqxEsJP_Zqz0cW0M6nKNO6gVI-g0V-iL_Dn7fk/edit#gid=674767160</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">6. 龍谷課金匯率?</span><br />\n答: MYCARD / GO卡都係1:1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">7. 練等攻略?</span><br />\n冇統一攻略, 正常流程係:<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1LV - 24LV</div><br />\n跟主線係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">凱德拉關卡</span>打<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">24LV - 40LV</div><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TlDQ7K7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTlDQ7K7.jpg&h=ea7fb79d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">黑山山腳</span>打任何關上40<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">40LV - 60 LV</div><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/r5cU86a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fr5cU86a.jpg&h=ee187dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">利伯偉特停泊處</span>上60<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">60LV - 80LV</div><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XiNhndh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXiNhndh.jpg&h=f0fa09c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">阿露亞倫戴關卡</span>上80<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">80LV - 93LV</div><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HduP59V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHduP59V.jpg&h=74d8f751&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分別去<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">梅露卡之心</span>打徐風上90<br />\n然後去<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">拉達梅斯</span>上93封頂<br />\n<br />\n亦可參考此處: <a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/dnbelief/home/leveling\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Fdnbelief%2Fhome%2Fleveling&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=89c2f9c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/site/dnbelief/home/leveling</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">8. 太完美係邊?</span><br />\n答: 係到<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/bxPOhc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbxPOhc0.jpg&h=45b8b9fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n80LV 之後 太完美會有每日任, 可以去換...有幾正自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hNlSvYy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhNlSvYy.jpg&h=31765ecb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n混沌遠征紋章數值:<br />\n<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/dnbelief/home/advanced/chaosplate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Fdnbelief%2Fhome%2Fadvanced%2Fchaosplate&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=9cfe2b15\" target=\"_blank\">https://sites.google.com/site/dnbelief/home/advanced/chaosplate</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9. 93LV之後可以做乜?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n打每日任務, 搵佢接任<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Fzc5By5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFzc5By5.jpg&h=a7674063&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打巢穴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n時空庭院位置<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ftndtXk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FftndtXk.jpg&h=07b1b26a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 10. 浸溫泉? </span><br />\n答: <br />\n可以到神聖天堂去農場搵溫泉NPC入去溫泉區<br />\n<br />\n有咩用? 效果如下:<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qNC6C86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqNC6C86.jpg&h=87cbefce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a32a12a1e0a26bcf93ef51eeca4921a961b49589","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 11. 無聊有咩做? </span><br />\n答: <br />\n淋花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/nDjwdVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnDjwdVc.jpg&h=3b0a9909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同蘿莉浸溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wN5sngh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwN5sngh.jpg&h=4485d2f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 12. 限時龍巢無得復活? </span><br />\n答: <br />\n綠龍 可以用 希望之花<br />\n森林龍 每過1關 會全隊復活<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">常用術語</span></span></div><br />\n組隊／頻道嘅時候成日見到：<span style=\"color: gold;\">93A 90S 80L 90L</span>，究竟係咩嚟呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前面數字代表<span style=\"color: orange;\">人物</span>等級　後面英文字代表<span style=\"color: orange;\">裝備</span>等級<br />\n用下面幅圖嚟講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅框框住　正正代表英文字嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\">裝備等級</span><br />\n由最左開始，分別係　Ｄ　<span style=\"color: green;\">Ｃ</span>　<span style=\"color: blue;\">B</span>　<span style=\"color: orange;\">Ａ</span>　<span style=\"color: purple;\">Ｓ</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">Ｌ</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ioqUrgH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FioqUrgH.jpg&h=1eece345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時組隊亦都會見到其他術語：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1帶7／2帶6</span>：隊伍由1個人(高手)帶隊　帶7個人通關過巢　如此類推<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">躺過</span>：打巢時死咗訓係到通關<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">站經</span>：０死站住通關的經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咩係任骰／關骰?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">任骰</span>：剔第1格　所有野都有機會靠擲骰仔獲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">關骰</span>：剔第2格　所有野都冇份擲骰唔關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2個都唔剔呢？到時就會每一樣物品都問你骰唔骰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圖解　見下圖<span style=\"color: red;\">紅框</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3n9cSed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3n9cSed.jpg&h=e0465ce6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7b89e2e9693d027d53d2a44fb0fb047953139a1","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:15:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 新龍之谷 連登公會資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong> </span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GW60ZLL.png?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGW60ZLL.png%3F1&h=ae331a38&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">古乳有云: 有巨龍嘅地方，就有連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋公會亦唔例外，冇45cm唔俾入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (真)絲打除外<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>[center]申請公會流程:</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n先按G (預設鍵)，會彈出公會列表<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7AmMQXb.jpg?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7AmMQXb.jpg%3F1&h=6695e442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後搜尋連登<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/W3kiQdA.jpg?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW3kiQdA.jpg%3F1&h=fc110925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按申請加入即可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uonuAzD.jpg?1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuonuAzD.jpg%3F1&h=1b4da2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n申請後回po通知我哋game名，耐心地等候我哋處理申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成功入會後請查閱公會公告，務必登記進入whatsapp群組同RC群<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登公會歡迎大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> </span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">最後感謝所有有提供過以上資料嘅連登巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無言感激 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">-聲明-</span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">維護公會聲譽你我有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，請避免作出不誠實或意圖行騙行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一經發現驅逐處分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">-以上資料僅作參考用途，玩家需因應龍谷環境轉變而作出適當/對應的評估，避免冒受損失，本會恕不負責。小心駛得萬年船，如有疑問，可以回覆查詢-</div>"},{"pid":"67fb1e32741c6a7bb2b6216394412daca77d18ae","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49dfdb0e21536d2aa08e9164368646d7798e7870","tid":795914,"uid":95555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"咁撚得閒連啲資料都update埋"},{"pid":"0d042fd3a370fa303cbb6075dea4b4e8d8f86596","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/27/eiFN2q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2FeiFN2q.jpg&h=aaff930e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebc229a7fd4e32009b8faaf21dd9f4e8a09c09cc","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49dfdb0e21536d2aa08e9164368646d7798e7870","tid":795914,"uid":95555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:18:07.000Z","msg":"咁撚得閒連啲資料都update埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f41fad138c217d28983e8617f94138a0e05f1d","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"我屌 多左個CENTER"},{"pid":"0f91021aff104a9e3e5d0cdf69b84198f3439906","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:20:11.000Z","msg":"想斬PO"},{"pid":"d022d9e1b6f02c797a07d9e465c530d240448ff0","tid":795914,"uid":193182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:22:16.000Z","msg":"點做野架"},{"pid":"6cc02f29756306eb460e1449c9e3a1350733a3a8","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d022d9e1b6f02c797a07d9e465c530d240448ff0","tid":795914,"uid":193182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:22:16.000Z","msg":"點做野架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:22:44.000Z","msg":"斬PO可以嗎"},{"pid":"42c70918768166720e9a0e5112cd7f4328132cf4","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cc02f29756306eb460e1449c9e3a1350733a3a8","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d022d9e1b6f02c797a07d9e465c530d240448ff0","tid":795914,"uid":193182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:22:16.000Z","msg":"點做野架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:22:44.000Z","msg":"斬PO可以嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37413e2975f93b7a08ab09b40b744137c26bacb8","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:24:30.000Z","msg":"斬PO 開新PO"},{"pid":"7fcbd26b44d4c189a2f10ee53c23bd1d6621675a","tid":795914,"uid":193182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"想問下93之後打咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1887dc05cefa19e007cf26fa7c15ed215a998b32","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7fcbd26b44d4c189a2f10ee53c23bd1d6621675a","tid":795914,"uid":193182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:24:53.000Z","msg":"想問下93之後打咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:26:20.000Z","msg":"米撚打"},{"pid":"0e68bce2f2c2f2a5adc23ce3b7bbcf3fd547627e","tid":795914,"uid":193182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"貢渣就5巧kai拉"},{"pid":"d89d0805b747244296397ca35561fa2634ec9e62","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:30:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/795931/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/795931/page/1</a><br />\n此PO已斬"},{"pid":"2b9bb96b72f96614e6452a386288df78a734089f","tid":795914,"uid":67177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"邊撚個有4階+20呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93b68041fb5d818ec85cdadf47bbe37a9653b5f","tid":795914,"uid":6654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b9bb96b72f96614e6452a386288df78a734089f","tid":795914,"uid":67177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"邊撚個有4階+20呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"斬撚左PO<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/795931/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/795931/page/1</a>"}]}